Class StreetLevelLink

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.common.ViewObject
      • com.here.android.mpa.streetlevel.StreetLevelProxyObject
        • com.here.android.mpa.streetlevel.StreetLevelLink
  • Deprecated. 
    Street Level APIs are deprecated As of SDK 3.7.

    @Deprecated
public final class StreetLevelLink
extends StreetLevelProxyObject
    Represents a class for all street level link objects used to follow from StreetLevel to StreetLevel within an on-screen SupportStreetLevelFragment. The street level link is visualised as a navigation arrow.
    See Also:
    StreetLevelModel.getSelectedObjects(PointF)
